$Id$

BUILDING

    In order to buid this package(s), execute the following:
    szn-buildpackage

    The package(s) will be built in `debian/build' directory, checked by
    Package Unit Test, and than moved to `debian/pkg'.

    If you left the build tree (parameter -l), you can debug packaging
    in directory debian/build using:
    fakeroot dpkg-buildpackage

MODIFYING

    To prepare Makefiles in this package(s) for development, execute:
    szn-preparepackage

    Do not forget to report your change to `debian/changelog' (to ease
    this process you can use `sdch' alias `szn-debchange')

    To clean the development tree you can use:
    fakeroot debian/rules clean

